      <title>美国股市在高标准财报季面临现实考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/the-stock-market-faces-reality-check-in-high-bar-earning-season</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着各家公司开始公布季度业绩，美国股市经历了两年来最强劲的反弹，现在正面临下一个重大考验，这将对估值是否超出基本现实提供重要的判断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/the-stock-market-faces-reality-check-in-high-bar-earning-season</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克称 Neuralink 已为第三名患者植入大脑设备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/musk-says-neuralink-implanted-third-patient-with-brain-device</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Neuralink Corp. 的脑机设备已植入第三名患者体内，该公司创始人埃隆·马斯克表示，该公司计划在 2025 年再植入约 20 至 30 例。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/musk-says-neuralink-implanted-third-patient-with-brain-device</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 03:18:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
